page.title: 20CONCLUSION
page.content: We have enjoyed working together and learning from each other and we have been able to identify many changes in our area over time. As for the future, we believe that the Grahame Park Estate may be given a new name. It will be interesting to see how and in what ways the new Superstores and large shopping centres in neighbouring blocks affect the shops in our area. How will the projects and amenities that we have described,be further changed and developed? St.James Catholic High Sch.-Class 1o Grahame Park Junior Sch. Colindale JMI.
